DefaultChoiceDisplayText.SourceString: Can you tell me about Ashenfall?
DefaultChoiceDisplayText.LocalizedString: Can you tell me about Ashenfall?

Message.SourceString: Keep your wits about you, young pup. Ashenfall is home to many a dangerous beast, and I've not yet tested my blade against each of them.
Message.LocalizedString: Keep your wits about you, young pup. Ashenfall is home to many a dangerous beast, and I've not yet tested my blade against each of them.

Message.SourceString: Well met, young pup. Seems like you haven't managed to cook that rat roast for me yet. You can get them by killing giant rats and cooking their meat. You can find some up by the windmill.
Message.LocalizedString: Well met, young pup. Seems like you haven't managed to cook that rat roast for me yet. You can get them by killing giant rats and cooking their meat. You can find some up by the windmill.

Message.SourceString: Well met, young pup. Looking to get yourself ready to face off against a dragon? You'll need more than that butter knife to kill one, but you've got to start somewhere.
Message.LocalizedString: Well met, young pup. Looking to get yourself ready to face off against a dragon? You'll need more than that butter knife to kill one, but you've got to start somewhere.

Message.SourceString: It may not exactly be gourmet cooking, but a meal like this could make the difference between life and death. You'll not be taking on any dragons if you're starving to death.
Message.LocalizedString: It may not exactly be gourmet cooking, but a meal like this could make the difference between life and death. You'll not be taking on any dragons if you're starving to death.

Message.SourceString: Well met, young pup. Looking to get yourself ready to face off against a dragon? You'll need more than that potato masher to kill one, but you've got to start somewhere.
Message.LocalizedString: Well met, young pup. Looking to get yourself ready to face off against a dragon? You'll need more than that potato masher to kill one, but you've got to start somewhere.

Message.SourceString: My name is Vannaka and back on the mainland I was a Slayer Master. It was my job to send adventurers after dangerous beasts.
Message.LocalizedString: My name is Vannaka and back on the mainland I was a Slayer Master. It was my job to send adventurers after dangerous beasts.

Message.SourceString: Cull the population of monsters, to make the world a better place.
Message.LocalizedString: Cull the population of monsters, to make the world a better place.

Message.SourceString: I was finding things a little stale on the mainland. When I saw the posters for the expedition, I felt a pull... a call to adventure that I could not resist.
Message.LocalizedString: I was finding things a little stale on the mainland. When I saw the posters for the expedition, I felt a pull... a call to adventure that I could not resist.

Message.SourceString: Be ready to fight, that's my first piece of advice. Craft armour, weapons and anything else you need for battle.
Message.LocalizedString: Be ready to fight, that's my first piece of advice. Craft armour, weapons and anything else you need for battle.

Message.SourceString: There are goblins everywhere in Bramblemead and deadlier things beyond.
Message.LocalizedString: There are goblins everywhere in Bramblemead and deadlier things beyond.

Message.SourceString: Past Bramblemead is Ghornfell, a place of danger and excitement. Something calls to me out there and I intend to seek it out.
Message.LocalizedString: Past Bramblemead is Ghornfell, a place of danger and excitement. Something calls to me out there and I intend to seek it out.

Message.SourceString: Getting ahead of yourself, aren't we, young pup? Check your map to see where you're meant to be headed.
Message.LocalizedString: Getting ahead of yourself, aren't we, young pup? Check your map to see where you're meant to be headed.

Message.SourceString: Properly cook a rat roast and bring them back to me. You'll probably burn a few along the way, don't let that disuade you. No one said survival would be pretty.
Message.LocalizedString: Properly cook a rat roast and bring them back to me. You'll probably burn a few along the way, don't let that disuade you. No one said survival would be pretty.

Message.SourceString: Right, let's teach you a bit about magic. Zanik's the one to talk to for that, you can find her down the road just before the river.
Message.LocalizedString: Right, let's teach you a bit about magic. Zanik's the one to talk to for that, you can find her down the road just before the river.

Message.SourceString: You will find rats are annoyingly resilient to clubs. Some enemies can resist certain damage types and be vulnerable to others.
Message.LocalizedString: You will find rats are annoyingly resilient to clubs. Some enemies can resist certain damage types and be vulnerable to others.

Message.SourceString: Rats, for example, don't take kindly to getting stabbed. Here, take this little butterknife to make it easier to fight them in future. You can have this as well, it'll help you with what's next.
Message.LocalizedString: Rats, for example, don't take kindly to getting stabbed. Here, take this little butterknife to make it easier to fight them in future. You can have this as well, it'll help you with what's next.

Message.SourceString: Look, you may have a weapon, but every great warrior knows wars are won by the stomach, not the blade.
Message.LocalizedString: Look, you may have a weapon, but every great warrior knows wars are won by the stomach, not the blade.

Message.SourceString: Behind me, up that little hill, is a windmill infested with rats. I want you to kill some of them and cook their meat.
Message.LocalizedString: Behind me, up that little hill, is a windmill infested with rats. I want you to kill some of them and cook their meat.

Message.SourceString: Hrmm, seems you're carrying the weight of the world right now. Come see me again when you've got some space free in your backpack.
Message.LocalizedString: Hrmm, seems you're carrying the weight of the world right now. Come see me again when you've got some space free in your backpack.

Message.SourceString: Don't pull that face, you can't be a picky eater in a place like this. Food will make you healthier and heartier, and much more likely to survive.
Message.LocalizedString: Don't pull that face, you can't be a picky eater in a place like this. Food will make you healthier and heartier, and much more likely to survive.

Message.SourceString: Well met, young pup. Seems your hunt was successful, I see you've gathered the food I asked for.
Message.LocalizedString: Well met, young pup. Seems your hunt was successful, I see you've gathered the food I asked for.
